2)], supporting the\nscenario of universality of buoyancy-driven turbulence with respect to the\ndifferent boundary conditions characterizing the RT and RB systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Aug 2013 12:46:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
